    "body":  "**Description:** We need to implement the core \"Opportunity\" defined in the vision: extracting structured data from unstructured documents. The system must allow users to upload PDF/Word documents (CVs, training certs) and use an AI service to parse them into JSON.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n[ ] User can upload a file (PDF, DOCX) via the frontend.\n[ ] Backend sends the file to an AI service (e.g., Azure OpenAI or Document Intelligence).\n[ ] System extracts the following fields: Skill Name, Date Acquired, Expiration Date, Issuing Authority.\n[ ] Extracted data is saved to the database linked to the user\u0027s profile.\n\n**Context for Copilot:**\nUse Azure Blob Storage for temporary file holding.\nUse a prompt strategy that asks the LLM to return strictly valid JSON.\nCreate a Mongoose/SQL schema for UserQualification that matches the extracted fields.",
